# List of vulnerability IDs to be ignored by Trivy.

# Please provide a comment with each vulnerability ID describing why it has been ignored.

# @octokit/plugin-paginate-rest, @octokit/request, @octokit/request-error -
# ReDoS in devDependency `auto` (release automation only, not shipped).
# Every fixed release of plugin-paginate-rest requires @octokit/core >=5, a
# breaking major bump from the v3.x that @auto-it/core's own code was written
# against; forcing it risks a runtime crash during an actual release, which
# is worse than the vulnerability itself (auto only parses GitHub's own
# trusted API responses, not attacker-controlled input). Revisit once auto
# ships a release that bumps its own @octokit dependencies.

CVE-2025-25288
CVE-2025-25289
CVE-2025-25290
